  "impact_on_program": {
    "Mpad": "Structural: multipad cores intersect in \u2264 free_core\u22121 points; free_core=1 packing recovered; deployed binomial packing useless",
    "kappa": "Need constructive residual highs\u21aa[2176]; naive tags banked negative",
